EmailTemplate.textOnly:
I have received several questions lately:
When are the next classes offered by Sunpower for Sales/Install/Design training?
Please review and save the attached document that will clearly describe to you how to find the most current available and the locations for Sunpower Training classes....
If you are at 40% closing ratio and you increase to ONE MORE out of TEN then you would see your income increase by 25%.
Thank You for your attention and let's register for classes to close that one more out of 10...
